    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KIRU KIRU KIRU is a fast-paced 2D arena shooter inspired by DOOM and ULTRAKILL.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In particular, it is a bloody, ultra-fast slasher about crowd control</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many enemies actively attack and you need to maneuver between them to prevent them from attacking, restore yourself with their blood, dodge their attacks and prioritize your targets:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/f9a1b079318c0de23fd0100871e31ab6.poster.avif?t=1755011437\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/f9a1b079318c0de23fd0100871e31ab6.webm?t=1755011437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/f9a1b079318c0de23fd0100871e31ab6.mp4?t=1755011437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/46baa0e3c440b271eec7fcdbfe9ccbad.poster.avif?t=1755011437\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/46baa0e3c440b271eec7fcdbfe9ccbad.webm?t=1755011437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/46baa0e3c440b271eec7fcdbfe9ccbad.mp4?t=1755011437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Redirecting attacks to opponents with melee hit:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/60de388731a6e62e84afbaa098246a5d.poster.avif?t=1755011437\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/60de388731a6e62e84afbaa098246a5d.webm?t=1755011437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2196030/extras/60de388731a6e62e84afbaa098246a5d.mp4?t=1755011437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Rip and cut</i> mutants, robots, ghosts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride along the walls and ceiling, dash through the enemies, dodge their attacks and make their <u>blood</u> flow. </p>",
